headline: JACK HENRY & ASSOCIATES TO PROVIDE WEBCAST OF FIRST QUARTER FISCAL 2026 EARNINGS CALL
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc.® (NASDAQ: JKHY) announced today that it will host a live Webcast of its first quarter fiscal year 2026 earnings conference call on November 5, 2025. The press release announcing first quarter fiscal 2026 earnings will be issued after market close on November 4, 2025.
